Package: RegCompassR
Title: Multiome-Supported Reaction Capacity and GRN Meta-Module Analysis
Version: 1.4.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Description: Runs a strict condition-by-sample-by-cell-type RNA+ATAC workflow in which each upstream worker completes SuperCell metacells, metacell LinkPeaks, Layer 1 evidence, Pando regulatory inference, and GRN-defined meta-modules. After all retained strata pass a global barrier, expression-derived reaction capacities are recalculated across all metacells, meta-modules are combined into one shared Human-GEM structure per medium, and metacell-specific penalties are evaluated with directional microCOMPASS optimization.
